OpenCV 2.0.0 Dependencies/Extras:
	* sudo apt-get install libavformat-dev libswscale-dev (from OpenCV Wiki)
	* ffmpeg ffmpeg-dbg libavdevice52 libavfilter0
	* libgstreamer0.10-dev
	* zlibc
	* libtiff4-dev libtiffxx0c2
	* libjasper-dev (JPEG-2000)
	* libunicap2 libunicap2-dev libxv-dev x11proto-video-dev
		(unified interface to video capture devices)
	* libgtk2.0-dev
	* libglib2.0-0-dbg
